        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "fifteen.) But He saw that, even from a human standpoint, the nation could not be helped in this way, and that the Jews would only rebel against the romans to their destruction.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "The Roman soldiers hesitated, but the Jews promised most faithfully to keep their word.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "But a furious madness had possessed the people, and they refused to yield.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "Josephus pleaded in vain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "He was not a Christian, but he could see plainly enough that God was no longer with His people.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "'Ah, my countrymen,' he cried, 'we did nothing without God in the past, but now you are fighting against Him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "At last the end came.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "The first wall fell, then the second and the third, until the Roman soldiers, now as mad as the Jews themselves, burst into the Holy City, hewing down the defenceless people at every step.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "'These Jews are dangerous.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "These explanations, all collected together, are called 'The Talmud.' Now the learned Jews grew so fond of their Talmud, that they declared a man to be a blockhead if he knew only the Scriptures and not the Talmud explanation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "'The law of Moses is like salt, but the Talmud is balmy spice,' they would say.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "'The ink you write with must be of a pure black, made only from a mixture of soot, charcoal, and honey.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000046_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000046_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "Though you know the whole Book of the Law by heart, you must not write a single word from memory, but raise your eyes to your copy, and pronounce the word aloud before trusting it to your pen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000046_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000046_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "If, after your copy has itself been examined, three corrections have to be made, that copy must be destroyed.'",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000048_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000048_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "The letter 'A'--that is the Hebrew letter which stands for 'A'--occurs forty two thousand three hundred seventy seven times; the letter 'B' thirty five thousand two hundred eighteen, and so on.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "Every sheet of parchment must contain an equal number of lines, and the breadth of each column had to be thirty letters wide.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "Just so was it with the Hebrew copies of God's Word.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_24512_000054_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5390/24512/5390_24512_000054_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5390",
        "content": "Locked up in a dead language, kept close, away from the world, they were like the jar of wheat which could not grow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5390_30096_000001_000000",
